{"tid":1924913,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"新增警員靠北方？","createTime":"2020-03-14T04:02:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-19T06:48:07.000Z","uid":81228,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"cc47031a1d6111230d2628f23d15e94da2699528","tid":1924913,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T04:02:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.inmediahk.net/files/styles/w775/public/column_images/20200313po2.jpg?itok=WXa3E8ub\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Ffiles%2Fstyles%2Fw775%2Fpublic%2Fcolumn_images%2F20200313po2.jpg%3Fitok%3DWXa3E8ub&h=75897d05&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n陳茂波在預算案中批准警察來年增加約2500人，佔全體新增公務員人數約6000人的40%。知法犯法卻得到整個政府包庇，行私刑冇後果，今天還獲准加人加錢，當然引起社會公憤。但數字也帶出另一個疑問：香港警察哪裏找這麼多人入行？<br />\n<br />\n警務處未來一年總人數預計增加7%至38406人，當中前線行動計劃增加約2000人、前線專業支援增加約230人、後勤增加約120人不等。<br />\n<br />\n大家要留意，警務處要達到增加2500人的目標，需新聘人手遠遠不止2500。根據去年財政預算案的數字（第485頁），警隊平均每年流失接近1200人，當中750左右是退休，其餘則是辭職、死亡或被革職等。因此警務處未來一年實際要聘請的人數約為3700。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>3700人從哪裏來？</strong><br />\n<br />\n1﹞首先當然是招聘和訓練本地新人。可以請到多少？去年財政預算案的數字（第589頁）指，黃竹坑警察學院每年訓練的學警和見習督察人數約1500人；<br />\n<br />\n2﹞另外是復聘剛退休警員留任。去年年底方向報報導：「警方估計至明年三月，將有約二千名職級由警員至總督察不等的人員退休或即將退休，警隊計劃復聘當中最少半數人力。」<br />\n<br />\n1500新入職警察 + 1000退休復職警察 = 2500人。還差1200人才「達標」。<br />\n<br />\n萬一在本地找不夠「足夠兵力」怎麼辦？眾所周知，香港這個「（殖民地）法治社會」，法例總是給予特首無限彈性達成目標，無人能阻。《公安條例》第40條就賦權林鄭可授權警務處長鄧炳強委任任何人做「特務警察」，包括名正言順聘請大陸執法人員來港鎮壓示威，權責與其他警務人員一樣。<br />\n<br />\n如此推演，預算案批准警隊整體人數新增2500人，難道是為「北兵南調」埋下伏線？<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg4-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/s960x960/89257791_2825817597484146_6701812650227007488_o.jpg?_nc_cat=107&amp;_nc_sid=8024bb&amp;_nc_ohc=WPlCXvsNqqcAX9x65CO&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg4-1.fna&amp;_nc_tp=7&amp;oh=58bc256aa71e5972f7c002b3dec0730d&amp;oe=5E8FB824\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg4-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2Fs960x960%2F89257791_2825817597484146_6701812650227007488_o.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D107%26_nc_sid%3D8024bb%26_nc_ohc%3DWPlCXvsNqqcAX9x65CO%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg4-1.fna%26_nc_tp%3D7%26oh%3D58bc256aa71e5972f7c002b3dec0730d%26oe%3D5E8FB824&h=17f6735d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n朱凱廸<br />\n新界西立法會議員<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.inmediahk.net/node/1071525\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1071525&d=B95HL5QQ1MLE%2FldfuzA7jxZ9qy%2BOiqBAJcOKDokr%2FlY%3D&h=79146478\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1071525&h=e2d9c452\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.inmediahk.net/node/1071525</a>"},{"pid":"a63991ecc1c1e585eeb9946442e8b65b80f337eb","tid":1924913,"uid":89349,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T05:42:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iqeHSBn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiqeHSBn.jpg&h=ab0b2641&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n屍Ben Sir<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n警務人員子女關注組<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1870807\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1870807</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"5dca47d25aece086ae3f9801d8ed493bd3e0024d","tid":1924913,"uid":18552,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T06:31:28.000Z","msg":"遲下連d 狗都無工開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7549e5e154b5b9aceb9109f2188e3ea0894225aa","tid":1924913,"uid":85327,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T07:13:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bf2d0db7b5dc4ae7315389e8502c1134188ea99d","tid":1924913,"uid":85327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T07:23:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2f67febf434d66de180e4ae5e1494972441b3e0d","tid":1924913,"uid":227271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T07:41:00.000Z","msg":"人工只係十分一<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />無得輸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />炒一個散仔請到十個喎，炒一隻大狗請到二三十個，何樂而不為<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76fdf2e10be2b38fc5f0464fd7f000a720c4caf5","tid":1924913,"uid":95059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T07:41:52.000Z","msg":"支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c125aec8fa3e18a615cab87f447c4ab8db8d75ff","tid":1924913,"uid":53700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T07:43:22.000Z","msg":"condom"},{"pid":"8ecbb8f845632465ed6985648d9fb50d481a8c6d","tid":1924913,"uid":109462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T07:46:57.000Z","msg":"「這是正式錄用的警察嗎？」<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e8463d88e2f4c8a2a9738004b83e4b57d79a046","tid":1924913,"uid":40779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T07:49:47.000Z","msg":"有槍我至大<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbe29942cce28db001a4e2501acec612185986bb","tid":1924913,"uid":106140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T07:51:32.000Z","msg":"直接喺堂口搵人入囉，vetting都唔洗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ec06c0e611868fa5cde4c4e2154316ff392c36b","tid":1924913,"uid":287422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T07:51:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ea4ba3ddb159e25067f1356c0593e0f8c75f3b0","tid":1924913,"uid":87780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T07:52:03.000Z","msg":"個社會咁畸形一定會有畜牲為咗份糧同福利走去做啦"},{"pid":"23a634bdb908d61f45dd14026f6f47da1b6dfb00","tid":1924913,"uid":250036,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T07:55:48.000Z","msg":"嘩賤"},{"pid":"1f38d10967e0fe98ca211f25028d5c5d25d5b47b","tid":1924913,"uid":3542